{"tid":933602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【通俄門】米勒︰特朗普前律師證實　有俄人曾提出助侵侵競選","createTime":"2018-12-08T15:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T04:12:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"510f376649b2f266ebbb1b53e1e418d222addd55","tid":933602,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181208/large/1544275680_c35a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181208%2Flarge%2F1544275680_c35a.jpg&h=623a16d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科恩作供曾有俄國人提出可協助特朗普選總統(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n美國「通俄案」特別檢察官米勒周五披露，早在2015年就有俄羅斯人聲稱可在特朗普競選總統時提供「政府級」協助。紐約聯邦檢察官亦首次指特朗普唆使前私人律師科恩，向兩名聲稱與特朗普有染的女子支付掩口費。分析指前者進一步證明俄羅斯意圖干預大選相助特朗普，但仍未構成串通證據，後者則將特朗普直接捲入涉嫌非法行為。<br />\n特朗普在2015年6月宣佈選總統，據米勒撰寫的法庭文件指，科恩同年11月與一名「獲俄羅斯聯邦信任」的俄籍人士對話，對方承諾向特朗普競選活動提供「政府級政治助力」，更多次提議特朗普會晤俄羅斯總統普京，指會面對政治或商業層面都有「非凡影響」。文件無公開該名俄國人的身份。<br />\n然而，米勒指會面最終未能成事，因科恩當時正與一名俄羅斯政府相關人士在一個項目合作，傳媒指此人應是有份參與莫斯科特朗普大樓計劃的發展商塞特（Felix Sater）。特朗普在米勒公開文件後，周六在Twitter「抽水」，揶揄米勒「經過2年及數百萬頁文件，沒有串通（證據）」。<br />\n科恩今年8月承認違反競選財務法、詐騙等8項罪名，早前更突然認假證罪，指向國會作供時稱莫斯科特朗普大樓計劃前年1月已停止，但事實到了6月進入大選競選期仍有聯絡。科恩亦承認受「1號人物」（特朗普的代號）指使，並在與之協調下支付掩口費。<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡/法新社  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181208/59008301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59008301&d=8SOQvrIox0hGW%2BDb74PY20bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=440a84a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59008301&h=ba52a8e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181208/59008301</a>"},{"pid":"a86f275e8ae095e122e30b7085618d7a4ce2c2aa","tid":933602,"uid":31475,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"連登繼續無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515888b5ba822a20bd7b8b8b7b7383d5146a3075","tid":933602,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a86f275e8ae095e122e30b7085618d7a4ce2c2aa","tid":933602,"uid":31475,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"連登繼續無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b90120f56c7b1e37347875e63fd41285b1159f3","tid":933602,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a86f275e8ae095e122e30b7085618d7a4ce2c2aa","tid":933602,"uid":31475,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"連登繼續無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:22:20.000Z","msg":"親俄一說早半年前已經破左功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b047611e85a27f14d4e4d98519dc94458349f0","tid":933602,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"515888b5ba822a20bd7b8b8b7b7383d5146a3075","tid":933602,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a86f275e8ae095e122e30b7085618d7a4ce2c2aa","tid":933602,"uid":31475,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"連登繼續無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"有證據咪告囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}